properties.name: Astoria Classic Restaurant
properties.desc:
Restaurant Astoria Classic is located in the trading centre of the city, close to the Central Department Store. It amazes with wide range of European cuisine and rich decoration of halls. Here you will plunge into the atmosphere of chic and grace. The restaurant consists of two halls on every separate floor of the restauraunt and can host up to 250-300 guests in total. Interior of halls (paintings and columns of emerald color) resembles the Malachite Hall in the Hermitage Palace, humpbacked bridges connect halls as if shores of Neva River.
In the evenings there is a music in disco style. At the daytime you will have launch to background music. Also you will be amazed with wide range of fruit desserts.

properties.name: Bakery in Orion Supermarket
properties.desc: General Mid-size Supermarket. But there is a takeout sweet bakery in the supermarket so that you can buy sweet slice cakes and tarts with cheep costs.

properties.name: Karimbek Restaurant
properties.desc: Cafe Karimbek is one of the popular venues among the other catering places of the Bek restauraunt chain. It is located in iranian mahalla, opposite the hotel "Tumaris". It has several halls, designed in national style. Here you can taste delicious national and European cuisine, wide range of shashliks. In the evenings you will see colorful show of Uzbek, Arab and European dances. Those who like quiet and privacy can make themselves comfortable in small private rooms, made in national style. During the warm season the guests are invited to its summer cafe.

properties.name: Lucky Cafe
properties.desc: Mini buffet restaurant. The advantage of buffet is that you can choose what you want with looking and pay by what you eat. Also slice cake for dessert and small pizza are prepared. If you are accompanied by kids, it's best place because there are free kiz zone in the restaurant.

properties.name: Marmar
properties.desc: It's not a big restaurant and also not prepared for international people. It' s just one of favorites of people who lives in around the place because of reasonable price and delicious food.  You can enjoy a few local foods like Samsa, Shashlik, Shurpa, etc. My recommendation here is the Uzbek style grilled chicken.

properties.name: Muborak-opa Restaurant
properties.desc: National House of Muborak-opa always welcomes guests of Samarkand. Here you will taste traditional Uzbek dishes. Hostess Muborak-opa pays special attention to different tastes of guests, including vegetarian menu. Here you will have an opportunity to get acquainted with national style of Uzbek house as well as with peculiarities of local cooking traditions. Oriental exotics, hospitality and comfortable rooms allow to have a good rest and gather strength before a trip. In addition you can order to prepare lunch-boxes for your journey.

properties.name: Old City Restaurant
properties.desc: Small homelike The Old City restaurant offers wide range of national, European and vegetarian dishes. Cozy atmosphere of restaurant, nice background music, hall with fireplace do not leave anyone indifferent. Visually the hall is divided into three zones. Restaurant Old City is the perfect place for lunches or dinners of small tourist groups. It is located not far from Alekseevskiy Cathedral and Zeravshan Hotel. Good cuisine, nice and homelike interior will remain in your memory.

properties.name: Platan Restaurant
properties.desc:
Original design of the restaurant Platan does not leave indifferent anyone. Decoration of the interior is made of natural materials (stone, wood). Uzbek and European cuisine, good service, abundance of interesting details, making the interior more elegant – all these things create the unique spirit of the restaurant Platan.
The restaurant has two halls, including small non-smoking hall. In the evenings live music of saxophone and piano sounds. Also there is winter garden and small artificial waterfall in the main hall. The restaurant Platan offers to taste dishes of national, European and vegetarian cuisine. The restaurant is located in the european part of the city, close to GUM store. Visiting Samarkand, do not miss an opportunity to visit the restaurant Platan.

properties.name: Registan Restaurant
properties.desc: Restaurant Registan is very attractive for tourists due to its location opposite to Registan Square. The restaurant offers wide range of dishes of national, European and vegetarian cuisine. The hostess, biologist by profession, and her daughter, historian, also prepared special menu for tourists – healthy eating followers. The restaurant has one common hall and two ayvans (bed trestles). Also at the restaurant there is the guest room for rest and overnight stay.

properties.name: Sabina
properties.desc: This restaurant has a specialty of Samarkand style "Plov" which is one of the most famous local dish in Uzbekistan. In Samarkand, the "Plov" is called to "Osh". Only menu of this restaurant is "Osh". Because already this is very famous for it, it's enough to sell only one menu.

properties.name: Samarkand Restaurant
properties.desc:
The Samarkand restaurant located in the same-name city is one of the popular places to hold white tie lunches and dinners. Located in the center of Samarkand, it is found near the Winemaking Museum named after Khovrenko, and not far from the Grand Samarkand and Grand Samarkand Superior hotels. 
The restaurant consists of two halls. The ground floor accommodates a huge hall decorated with painted walls and ceilings, the guest can enjoy the meal to Uzbek national music. On the first floor there is Russian Hall whose decoration is enriched with elements of traditional Russian culture: false bags with wheat, a maquette of well, chests, bear’s skin, dummy goatling and so on. 
The Samarkand restaurant offers Uzbek and European food; however the most popular dishes are jiz-biz and Samarkand pilaf. You will duly appreciate the cooks’ skills and certainly wish to come there again and again.

properties.name: Sezam
properties.desc: This restaurant has a specialty of Ragman which is local noodle dish in Uzbekistan. Already this restaurant is famous for it in this city. Delicious and reasonable price! This is one of my favorites. If you like a noodle dish, I strongly recommend you.

properties.name: Shirin Bakery
properties.desc: Western Style Bakery. Taste and quality is superior to general bakery, but can't be compared to those of advanced country. Nevertheless, if you want to find some sort of sweet slice cakes and tarts in this city, I can recommend you enough.

properties.name: Zafar
properties.desc: The advantage of this restaurant is almost no differences of a price between tourists and native people and english menu is prepared . Main dishes are manly barbecued meats. If you prefer a mutton, this is recommendable place for you. But this advantage here is 12% of tax rate.
